articles.title: Killing cancer takes guts: lessons learned from the manipulation of gut microbiome and immunotherapy for the future of urothelial carcinoma.
articles.summary: In urothelial carcinoma, specific gut bacteria can enhance immunotherapy effectiveness by boosting immune system responses and improving treatment outcomes.
